Created a basic brush tool using WebGl. Features several shapes to draw with as well as a way to change color and transparency.

Sources Used regarding blending and transparency

https://www.khronos.org/registry/OpenGL-Refpages/es2.0/xhtml/glBlendFunc.xml
https://medium.com/david-guan/alpha-blending-and-webgl-823d86de00d8
